        </p>
        <p>@Html.ActionLink("Check messages", "ListMessages", "Home", null, new { @class = "btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-sm-3" })</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Are you a developer?</h2>
        <p>You can add AI to your applications with Expert.AI.</p>

        <p> <a href="https://expert.ai/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-success btn-lg px-4">ExpertAI</a></p>
    </div>
</div>